MYSQL -RELATIONAL DATABASES :TABLES
MONGODB:NO-SQL DATABASES :KEY:VALUE PAIR
MONGODB IS OPEN SOURCE
MONGODB IS APPLICALE WHERE GRAPHS,TREES,DOCUMENTS
IN MONGODB TABLE WILL BE TREATED AS COLLECTION
IN EACH COLLECTION AN INDIVIDUAL RECORD CALLED AS DOCUMENT
IN MONGODB PRIMARY KEY IS AUTOMATICALLY GENERATED BY THE DATABASE
MONGO DB IS SCALABLE
MONGODB STORES THE DATA IN THE FORM OF JSON OR KEY:VALUE PAIR
JSON FORMAT IS VERY POPULAR TO TRANSMIT DATA BETWEEN ANY TWO ELECTRON:
AND API DATA FORMATS THROUGH HTTP
